<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>We received your inquiry</title>
  </head>
  <body style="margin:0;padding:32px;background-color:#f7f9fb;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;color:#0f172a">
    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" style="max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;background:#ffffff;border-radius:16px;padding:32px">
      <tr>
        <td>
          <p style="font-family:monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#64748b;margin:0 0 12px">Ployos · Contact</p>
          <h1 style="font-size:24px;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 16px">Hi <%= name %>, we got your message.</h1>
          <p style="margin:0 0 16px;color:#475569;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6">Thanks for reaching out about <strong><%= topicLabel %></strong>. A real human on our team will reply within twelve hours.</p>
          <p style="margin:0 0 24px;color:#475569;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6">In the meantime, you can reply directly to this email if you'd like to add anything.</p>

          <p style="margin:32px 0 0;font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8">© <%= year %> Ployos. This is an automated acknowledgement.</p>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
